# delegate

**Instance Property**

The cache’s delegate.

## Declaration

```swift
unowned(unsafe) var delegate: (any NSCacheDelegate)? { get set }
```

## Discussion

The delegate must adopt the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSCacheDelegate] protocol.

## Managing the Delegate

- **NSCacheDelegate**: The delegate of an [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSCache] object implements this protocol to perform specialized actions when an object is about to be evicted or removed from the cache.
